videos.description: Marques Bolden throws down an early jam as Duke and NC State are close in the early going.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bolden gets dunk party started early) 2019/2/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bolden gets dunk party started early

videos.description: Zion Williamson has a wide-open lane on his way to a big dunk against NC State.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play ( Zion left alone for monster jam) 2019/2/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zion left alone for monster jam

videos.description: Zion Williamson leads all scorers with 19 points as No. 2 Duke leads NC State at home 48-40 at the half.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Zion puts up 19 points in big 1st half for Duke) 2019/2/16 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Zion puts up 19 points in big 1st half for Duke

videos.description: The Blue Devils start the second half hot as Cam Reddish gets the crowd excited with a big baseline dunk.
videos.headline: Reddish throws down big baseline flush

videos.description: As Markell Johnson thinks he has the easy layup, Jack White comes out of nowhere and the crowd goes wild.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (White runs full length of court for crazy block) 2019/2/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: White runs full length of court for crazy block

videos.description: R.J. Barrett finds a wide-open Jack White who hammers home the lob in the second half.
videos.headline: Barrett finds White for big-time alley-oop

videos.description: DJ Funderburk jumps over Marques Bolden for a massive NC State alley-oop in the second half.
videos.headline: Funderburk throws down nasty alley-oop

videos.description: Zion Williamson is all alone flying for the big two-handed dunk late in the second half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play ( Zion goes flying for two-handed slam) 2019/2/16

videos.headline: Zion goes flying for two-handed slam

videos.description: RJ Barrett records 23 points, 11 rebounds and 10 assists for only the fourth triple-double in Blue Devils history.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Barrett records 4th triple-double in Duke history) 2019/2/16 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Barrett records 4th triple-double in Duke history

videos.description: Zion Williamson says he's hoping to be competing against LeBron James and Steph Curry "next year."

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Interview (Zion: 'I guess it's dope' to be mentioned by LeBron and Steph) 2019/2/16

videos.headline: Zion: 'I guess it's dope' to be mentioned by LeBron and Steph
